A basic string hash function (djb2 algorithm) commonly used in C++ mappings:

```cpp
#include <string>

unsigned long GetHash(const std::string& Key) {
    unsigned long Hash = 5381;
    for (char C : Key) {
        Hash = ((Hash << 5) + Hash) + C; // Hash * 33 + C
    }
    return Hash;
}
```
